name: Consistent Care Services- COVID Vaccine Site
vaccines: Janssen COVID-19 Vaccine, Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 Vaccine
info: ***Joints for Jabs! In conjunction with Apex Cannabis, this is a clinic for 1st or 2nd doses of the Pfizer COVID-19 vaccine or the single dose of the Johnson & Johnson vaccine*** This clinic is located at Apex Cannabis at 1325 N. Division St., Suite 103. Please enter the building at the time of your appointment only. ***You will receive a free joint of your choice up to a $30 value with your vaccination whether it’s your first or 2nd dose. If you pre-register for your appointment you will also receive 25% off your purchase that day and if you are a walk-in appointment you’ll receive 15% off your purchase that day. ***Residents of ANY state are now eligible for the vaccine, but you still must have photo ID and be 21 or over to enter the building*** *VERY IMPORTANT* ***Please complete all the insurance/Medicare/Medicaid information when registering online for your appointment to avoid filling it out at the clinic**
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Yakima County Health District COVID Vaccination Site
info: ***1ST & 2nd DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS***!!!!VACUNAS DE PRIMERA Y SEGUNDA DOSIS PFIZER!!!! The vaccination clinic will take place at the Granger High School parking lot off of Mentzer Ave. This clinic will be drive-through. Masks are required. Please wear clothing which allows access to your shoulder. Vaccinations at this site are reserved for people who live and/or work in Washington State. All individuals 12 and over are eligible to get vaccinated. Those under 18 must be accompanied by a parent/guardian or must get parental consent via video/phone call or paper format. La clínica de vacunación se ubicara en el estacionamiento de la Escuela Secundaria de Granger, que se encuentra en la avenida Mentzer. Se requieren máscaras. Por favor, use ropa que permita acceso a su brazo. Las vacunas en este sitio están reservadas para las personas que viven o trabajan en el estado de Washington. Todas las personas mayores de 12 años son elegibles para vacunarse. Los menores de 18 años deben estar acompañados por un padre/tutor o deben obtener el consentimiento de los padres por video/llamada telefónica o en papel. ***1ST & 2nd DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS***!!!!VACUNAS DE PRIMERA Y SEGUNDA DOSIS PFIZER!!!!
